00:31:16.453 --> 00:31:19.070
he was reluctant.

00:31:19.070 --> 00:31:24.615
He was reluctant that he didn't
want to start writing the book.

00:31:24.615 --> 00:31:30.820
The reason why-- most
likely, this reminded him

00:31:30.820 --> 00:31:33.560
with all the bad memories.

00:31:33.560 --> 00:31:37.490
He saw a lot of his
friends during the war die.

00:31:37.490 --> 00:31:41.120
And it's so painful.

00:31:41.120 --> 00:31:44.980
And this happened to me too--
because a lot of emotion.

00:31:44.980 --> 00:31:47.270
Even now, when I say
about it, I still

00:31:47.270 --> 00:31:49.550
carry those emotions with me.

00:31:49.550 --> 00:31:54.320
But when Sharon talked to me
about it and that I should--

00:31:54.320 --> 00:31:56.220
I talked to him a few days.

00:31:56.220 --> 00:32:00.590
But we have to face it
somehow, one way or the other.

00:32:00.590 --> 00:32:02.050
We have to let it out.

00:32:02.050 --> 00:32:04.060
And after that, he
agreed that, OK,

00:32:04.060 --> 00:32:05.500
we can write a story about it.

00:32:05.500 --> 00:32:09.192
That's when Sharon came
to Bentonville, Arkansas.

00:32:09.192 --> 00:32:10.900
And she sat down and
interviewed with us.

00:32:10.900 --> 00:32:13.670
So that's why we overcome it.

00:32:13.670 --> 00:32:15.510
And my mom and my
brother and sister--

00:32:15.510 --> 00:32:17.150
they said, excited about it.

00:32:17.150 --> 00:32:23.770
They're really happy that
their story and our story

00:32:23.770 --> 00:32:27.550
just come to light and at
least share with everyone,

00:32:27.550 --> 00:32:32.170
that's how we've been through,
especially after the Vietnam

00:32:32.170 --> 00:32:33.190
War.

00:32:33.190 --> 00:32:36.930
And there wasn't a lot
of people outside Vietnam

00:32:36.930 --> 00:32:41.560
know about what the
life and how we lived

00:32:41.560 --> 00:32:43.980
under the communist rules--

00:32:43.980 --> 00:32:46.235
how we facing those.

00:32:46.235 --> 00:32:47.860
AUDIENCE: Thank you
so much for sharing

00:32:47.860 --> 00:32:49.900
