00:32:49.900 --> 00:32:51.880
I wanted to ask you,
what would your message

00:32:51.880 --> 00:32:55.750
be today for people who now
live under oppressive regimes,

00:32:55.750 --> 00:32:57.340
like the Viet Cong?

00:32:57.340 --> 00:33:00.760
How would you instill
hope within them

00:33:00.760 --> 00:33:02.810
that, someday,
things could change

00:33:02.810 --> 00:33:05.770
and they may have a happy life?

00:33:05.770 --> 00:33:09.190
THUHANG TRAN: That's
a great question.

00:33:09.190 --> 00:33:12.520
Again, you mentioned the hope--

00:33:12.520 --> 00:33:15.190
and I hope that whoever--

00:33:15.190 --> 00:33:19.810
they still live under
communism, not only Vietnam,

00:33:19.810 --> 00:33:22.750
but other countries as well--

00:33:22.750 --> 00:33:29.310
they need to continue
to have a purpose--

00:33:29.310 --> 00:33:33.930
their life purpose, not give up.

00:33:33.930 --> 00:33:38.760
Even though that is under
communism country or any other

00:33:38.760 --> 00:33:42.660
government, you need to
have a focus and find out,

00:33:42.660 --> 00:33:50.570
what is the meaning of their
life and how they can make

00:33:50.570 --> 00:33:54.550
small acts-- can
impact other people--

00:33:54.550 --> 00:34:00.210
and don't lose hope or
lose our focus on that--

00:34:00.210 --> 00:34:01.530
always seeking for a purpose.

