00:34:08.110 --> 00:34:08.610
Sharon--

00:34:08.610 --> 00:34:09.280
SHARON ORLOPP:
All right-- great.

00:34:09.280 --> 00:34:09.403
MODERATOR: Thank you.

00:34:09.403 --> 00:34:09.710
Thank you very much.

00:34:09.710 --> 00:34:10.480
SHARON ORLOPP: Let's appreciate
