out-- probably through Google.

00:42:13.120 --> 00:42:15.017
But he said, you-- you--

00:42:15.017 --> 00:42:16.350
I know what you do for a living.

00:42:16.350 --> 00:42:17.805
He said, I want to thank you.

00:42:17.805 --> 00:42:20.180
