our core values are.

00:42:32.720 --> 00:42:33.637
And how do we live it?

00:42:33.637 --> 00:42:36.900
And then, how do we share
their stories about it?

00:42:36.900 --> 00:42:42.940
So I'm going to click to
the second-to-last slide,

00:42:42.940 --> 00:42:44.150
