00:42:52.520 --> 00:42:54.040
But find out people's stories.

00:42:54.040 --> 00:42:56.110
Have curiosity
about other people.

00:42:56.110 --> 00:42:58.540
Find out what their story
is, and share your story.

00:42:58.540 --> 00:43:00.130
And then look for
those moments that

00:43:00.130 --> 00:43:01.900
